Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE GOD OF THE UNDERWORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I shall give you a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,These two will not intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall fight you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you won't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We would have fought even if you had\NMystban and the Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've all come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His ability to fight was magnificent\Nand he truly lived up to the legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But sadly, it seems his heart\Nwas far too human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me give him\Nan ending befitting a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Merazoma spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that unsatisfactory?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you wish to send him off yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. Your precious Hero\Nwas the first to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And now there's no one left\Nwith the power to harm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He took down Dai with one blow?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that power?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disappointment.\NAnd after I gave him a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You would follow your father, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Heal Dai\Nwhile I hold him off with my spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! He burned these clothes\Nthat were sewn with magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a tiny ember!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Dark King's Merazoma spell\Nthat much stronger than mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Merazoma spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was no Merazoma spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Mera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the same spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on the caster's Magic Power,\Nthe effects can vary greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, comparing my Mera spell\Nto your Merazoma spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,my spell is far more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a difference in strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to break the Dark Army's\Nassault time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I assumed you were\Na little more powerful, but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with that blow to Dai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely shot a little of my Aura\Nto match his attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Super-pressurized Dark Aura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He hit Dai with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look good!\NWe must fight as one if we want to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Dai?! Is Dai alright, Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart is beating.\NBut he took so much damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was hit where\Nhe'd already been wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just heal him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I enjoy\Nwatching you weaklings struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,don't bother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I was wrong\Nto give you a taste of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Dai was in your ranks,\Nit would change nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As recompense,\Nallow me to kill you painlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Merazoma spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,From its unimaginable power\Nand graceful form...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it has its own ancient name\Nin the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}Kaiser Phoenix.{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My armour should be able\Nto withstand it for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and heal Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A second one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! He's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Switch to the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King, prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Such bright eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How revolting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be far more magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please work!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can't beat him with this,\NI'll be out of spells that'll work on him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please work!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Medoroa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mahokanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to cancel it out!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! He reflected my spell\Nwith a Mahokanta spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use Medoroa anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he cast a Mahokanta spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,His magic is on a whole different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,His magic doesn't have a charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He can cast spells without\Ntaking the time to charge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That lets him do two things\Nin the time it takes us to do one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're attacking,\Nhe can attack and defend at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, can you carry Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking us over to Big Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll Rura out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hear any arguments this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he's called\Nthe God of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on a whole different level from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we are to fight him again,\Nwe'll need to regroup first or we'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.\NNow things are even more hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one escapes the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}MEDOROA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}KAISER PHOENIX{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban Palace is shielded\Nby King Ban's Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape it with a Rura spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving within Ban Palace\Nmay be possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but no one can enter\Nand no one may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No one but warriors of the Dark Army\Nblessed with a special spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Had you tried to fight instead of running,\Nmaybe you could have lived longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, there's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all done for! Done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you're all done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're! All! Done! For!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I grazed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}back then...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with my Refractor Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Back when you all attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shock. It's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It worked!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark King Ban is still\Na living creature!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can hit him with my Refractor Fist...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is indeed\Na one-in-a-million opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My servants won't intervene\Nand I'm wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My attacks will be slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, surely you know\Nthat Darklings can regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry,\Nyour opportunity will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't escape\Nand I'm the only one who can fight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to give it a shot!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, Maam! Do you really think\Nhe can be defeated so simply?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How very sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The little Mage is definitely\Nthe MVP of this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You were toying with me!\NYou could have regenerated any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel! Do you enjoy\Nplaying with us like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I do enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you use the awesome power\Nyou've gained to toy with the weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is it not pleasurable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not feel superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Power is the purest, most simple,\Nand most beautiful fundamental law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Might makes right"\Nis how all creatures live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Darklings... Dragons... All creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Only humans use their\Npompous reasoning to deny the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Power is the truth that rules all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you have power, that doesn't\Ngive you the right to disrupt peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The peace that everyone\Non the Surface World desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that peace is maintained\Nby a greater power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By the power of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My home, the Underworld, is a world\Nthat lies far beneath your lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere you look is\Nboiling magma and barren land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of all life,\Ndoes not shine in the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun... Such a magnificent power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But the gods granted the sun\Nand the Surface World to the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,banishing the Darklings\Nand Dragons to the Underworld
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,simply because the humans\Nwere weaker than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is justice,\Nthan our power, too, is justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I spent\Nthousands of years building my power
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in preparation to annihilate\Nthe Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, the Surface World will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, in our Underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the sun shall shine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall truly be God of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The folly committed by the gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,shall be rectified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-We can't win!\NHe's thinking on a whole different scale!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For thousands of years, he's thought of\Nthe Surface World as nothing but a lid!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're just...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're just mere humans!\NThere's no way we can hope to win!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was more enjoyable than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well,\NHeroes of the Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if everyone in the world does,\NI won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What impressive vitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was that?\NI don't think I heard you correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never give up.\NEven if everyone loses hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up until the very, very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I heard you correctly the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it inconceivable that you would\Nsay such a thing when faced with my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know just how overwhelming\Nyour power is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that power is justice,\Nbut you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what Grampa taught me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or what Master Aban taught me...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or what Dad taught me about justice!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong about everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They stand again?!\NAfter they were on the verge of death?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognize the power of your soul, which\Ngave your despairing friends strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't kill me with your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to change\Nmy mind about justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then use your power and not your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}Kaiser Phoenix!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He pierced it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was able to counter my second attack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only that, his force overpowered\Nmy Kaiser Phoenix and reached me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Iora spells?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's like a storm of Iora spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban's using weaker spells\Nand fighting with numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, each spell is\Nas destructive as a Ionazun spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban, perhaps you should\Nstop playing and let us all fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually believe that\Nhe will wound me further?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:12.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:18.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:23.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:29.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:35.60,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:47.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:53.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:59.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:01.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:10.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:16.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:22.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:30.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's Aban Strash blasts Ban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recognizing Dai's power, Dark King Ban\Nsummons a legendary weapon to counter him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its power shakes\Nthe heavens and the earth.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ban easily drives Dai back\Nand unleashes a finishing blow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Dai and his friends find hope\Nin the face of certain doom?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Unlikely Savior"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
